{
  "stem": "20684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They asked me if I could count and I could, but no longer on my hand.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now I could do it loudly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I would count up to 100 and if the feather didn't move, I went to the next one-- one or two, whatever they were numbers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If the feather moved, I called them over and they gave it another go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave him another bayonet just to finish off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Occasionally [INAUDIBLE] I learned my first year words in German during that time because there were some that were injured but they sort of survived a little bit longer and they had enough strength to still pull out photographs and they used to point out to their children-- kinder, frau; kinder, frau.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were showing me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were the first German words I learned, you know, trying to-- to sort of save their life or whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they explained to me that and I thought it was a bit cruel to kill a man that's got children and wives, but we knew where we were and what business we were because they took no prisoners and we took no prisoners.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, if we get caught, we get killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the-- the captain explained that ti's better that they die than we die.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "For every one of them that dies, one of us survives.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the game was good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then we took off the boots.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I used to carry the boots around my neck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We took off all the leather-- you know, belts and things like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If the clothing was good, we took that-- caps, this, that, and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We carried all the loot back with us and that was good fun.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I had a job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was-- I felt like being part of the machinery.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
